<module_design>
  <mt_id>MT-1</mt_id>
  <title>pipeline.py diff gate 신규 함수 + patch plan/audit/verify/attest 강화 + PIPELINE_CLUSTER_DIR + acceptance evidence 강화</title>
  <interface_contract>
    <input>pipeline_state.json, patch_plan.json, git repository</input>
    <output>pipeline_state.json (갱신), exit codes (0=pass, 1=fail)</output>
  </interface_contract>
  <implementation_plan>
    <step>1. _get_actual_diff_scope() 신규 함수 추가</step>
    <step>2. _cmd_patch_plan --base-ref 파라미터 추가, diff gate 호출</step>
    <step>3. _cmd_patch_audit diff gate 호출</step>
    <step>4. _cmd_patch_verify --test-command, --evidence-file 추가</step>
    <step>5. _cmd_patch_attest verify_passed 선행 확인</step>
    <step>6. _load_cluster_json/_save_cluster_json PIPELINE_CLUSTER_DIR 지원</step>
    <step>7. gates accept outputs_manifest 검증</step>
  </implementation_plan>
  <verification_plan>
    <test>python pipeline.py patch plan --skip-diff-check → exit 0</test>
    <test>python pipeline.py patch verify --result PASS (no evidence) → exit 1</test>
    <test>pytest tests/test_patch_lane.py 전체 PASS</test>
  </verification_plan>
</module_design>
